#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kalzium; is a program which shows you the Periodic Table of Elements. You "
"can use &kalzium; to search for information about the elements or to learn "
"facts about the periodic table."
msgstr ""
"&kalzium; je program koji prikazuje Periodni Sistem Elemenata. Možete "
"koristiti &kalzium; da tražite informacije o elementima ili da naučite "
"činjenice o periodnom sistemu."

#. Tag: keyword
