#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kalzium; main window</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kalzium; glavni prozor</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kalzium; main window</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kalzium; glavni prozor </phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kalzium; is divided in an information panel on the left (in red), the table "
"view (in blue) which shows the elements of the periodic table, and a legend "
"panel at the bottom (in green). The standard menubar allows you to choose "
"what you want to display and the status bar reports facts. The table view "
"and the panels can be hidden using the corresponding items in <guimenu>View</"
"guimenu> menu. For example, you can hide the information panel with "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Information</guimenuitem> "
"</menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"&kalzium; je podijeljen na informacijski panel lijevo ( u crvenom ), pregled "
"tabele ( u pravom ) koja prikazuje elemente periodnog sistema, i panel "
"legendi na dnu ( u zelenom ) . Standardna traka menija dozvoljava vam da "
"izaberete šta želite prikazati na statusnoj raportnoj traci činjenica. "
"Prikaz tabele i paneli mogu se sakriti koristeći odgovarajuće stavke u  "
"<guimenu>Prikaz</guimenu> meniju.\n"
"Na primjer, možete sakriti informacijski panel sa <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Prikaz</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Informacije</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you move the mouse cursor on an element of the table, an overview of "
"the current element is displayed in the <guilabel>Overview</guilabel> tab of "
"the information panel."
msgstr ""
"Kada želite pomjeriti kursor miša sa tabele, pregled trenutnog elementa je "
"prikazan u tabu <guilabel>Pregled</guilabel> informacijskog panela."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can choose several views for the table: classic periodic table, short "
"periodic table, long periodic table, &etc; It is also possible to change "
"numeration scheme or display the elements per families, per groups, per "
"crystal structure, depending on their acidic behavior, &etc; You can change "
"all that in the <guimenu>View</guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"Možete odabrati nekoliko prikaza za tabelu: klasični periodni sistem, kratki "
"periodni sistem, dugi periodni sistm, &etc; takože je moguće promijeniti "
"numeracju sheme ili prikazati elemente po familijama, po grupama, po "
"kristalnoj strukturi, zavisno od njihovog ponašanja kiselosti, &etc; Možete "
"promijeniti sve to u <guimenu>Prikaz</guimenu> meniju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to know facts about a precise element, click on it in the table "
"and the information dialog will be displayed."
msgstr ""
"Ako želite da znate činjenice o nekom elemenut, kliknite na njega na tabeli "
"i informacijski dijalog će biti prikazan."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Information dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Informacijski dijalog</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:116
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Information dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Informacijski dijalog</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:120
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You can plot data using the <menuchoice> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> "
#| "<guimenuitem>Plot Data...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> menu item. You "
#| "choose what you want to plot on the y-axis and a range of elements to "
#| "plot that for on the x-axis. The screenshot below shows the atomic mass "
