#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bohr Orbitals"
msgstr "Bohrove orbite"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Atom Model</guilabel> page displays the atomic shells. Every "
"orbit stands for a atomic shell and every yellow circle represents an "
"electron."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Model atoma</guilabel> stranica prikazuje atomske okvir. Svaka "
"orbita je atomski okvir i svaki žuti krug je elektron."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid "Isotopes"
msgstr "Izotopi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Isotopes</guilabel> page presents information about the "
"isotopes of an element."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Izotopi</guilabel> stranica prikazuje informacije o izotopima "
"elementa."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mass"
msgstr "Masa"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid "The mass of this isotope."
msgstr "Masa ovog izotopa."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid "Neutrons"
msgstr "Neutroni"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid "The number of neutrons this isotope has."
msgstr "Broj neutrona koje izotop ima."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid "Percentage"
msgstr "Procenat"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The percentage of atoms occurring that are of this isotope type. Also called "
"abundance."
msgstr "Procenat atoma koji su izotopi ovog tipa. Takođe se naziva obilnost."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid "Half-life period"
msgstr "Period poluraspada"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Only unstable isotopes have a half-life period. It is defined as the time in "
"which half the isotopes decay."
msgstr ""
"Samo nestablni izotopi imaju period poluraspada. On je definisan kao vrijeme "
"za koje se raspadne polovina izotopa."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid "Energy and Mode of Decay"
msgstr "Energija i režim raspada"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some isotopes are known to emit particle radiation under the process of "
"radioactive decay. Each decay transformation has a typical energy release, "
"which is listed along with the mode of decay."
msgstr ""
"Neki izotopi su poznati po tome što emituju radijacijsku česticu u toku "
"procesa radioaktivnog raspada. Svaka transformacija u obliku raspada "
"oslobađa određenu energiju, koja je prikazana zajedno sa načinom raspada."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid "Spin and Parity"
msgstr "Spin i paritet"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid "The spin of the nucleus and its parity."
msgstr "Spin jezgra i njegov paritet."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:248
#, no-c-format
msgid "Magnetic Moment"
msgstr "Magnetski moment"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The magnetic dipole moment of the nucleus. Measured in units of the nuclear "
"magneton."
msgstr ""
"Magnetski dipolski momenat jezgra. Mjeren u jedinicama nuklearnog megnetona."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:270
#, no-c-format
msgid "Miscellaneous"
msgstr "Razno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Miscellaneous</guilabel> page tells you other information "
"about the current element, including when it was discovered and the origin "
"of the name."
msgstr ""
"Stranica <guilabel>Razno</guilabel> vam govori ostale informacije o "
"trenutnom elementu, uključujući kada je otkriven i korijen imena."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid "Spectrum"
msgstr "Spektar"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Spectrum</guilabel> page shows you elements spectrum. You can "
"choose the range of the wavelengths, units and type of the spectrum. The "
"intensity table can be seen at the right bottom part of the page."
msgstr ""
"Stranica <guilabel>Spektar</guilabel> prikazuje spektar elemenata. Možete "
"odabrati rang talasnih dužina, jedinice i tip spektra. Tabela intenziteta je "
"vidljiva na donjem desnom dijelu stranice."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid "Extra Information"
msgstr "Dodatne Informacije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:306
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The <guilabel>Extra information</guilabel> page gives you the links to "
#| "the element pages on Wikipedia, <ulink url=\"http://education.jlab.org/"
#| "\">Jefferson Lab</ulink>, and <ulink url=\"http://www.webelements.com/"
#| "\">WebElements</ulink>."
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Extra information</guilabel> page gives you the links to the "
"element pages on Wikipedia, <ulink url=\"https://education.jlab.org/"
"\">Jefferson Lab</ulink>, and <ulink url=\"https://www.webelements.com/"
"\">WebElements</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Stranica <guilabel>Dodatne informacije</guilabel> daje vam linkove do "
"elemenata na Wikipediji, <ulink url=\"http://education.jlab.org/\">Jefferson "
"Lab</ulink>, i <ulink url=\"http://www.webelements.com/\">WebElements</"
"ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:323 index.docbook:798
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tables"
msgstr "Tabele"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The periodic table can be presented in various ways. You can switch the "
"table view from <guimenu>View</guimenu> menu or toolbar drop-down list."
msgstr ""
"Periodni sistem može biti prikazan na više načina. Možete promijeniti prikaz "
"tabele iz  <guimenu>Prikaz</guimenu> menija ili ispustiti-dolje liste alatne "
"trake."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:327
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The following options in the <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> "
#| "<guimenuitem>Tables</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu can be used to change "
#| "the table shown:"
msgid ""
"The following options in the <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Tables</guisubmenu></menuchoice> menu can be used to change the "
"table shown:"
msgstr ""
