#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:374
#, no-c-format
msgid "Numeration"
msgstr "Prebrojavanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:376
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The numeration is the way of numbering the 18 groups of the periodic table. "
"You can change the numeration to <guilabel>IUPAC</guilabel>, <guilabel>old "
"IUPAC</guilabel> or <guilabel>CAS</guilabel>, or you can switch it off "
"entirely."
msgstr ""
"Prebrojavanje je način numerisanja 18 grupa periodnog sistema. Možete "
"promijeniti prebrojavanje u <guilabel>IUPAC</guilabel>, <guilabel>old IUPAC</"
"guilabel> ili <guilabel>CAS</guilabel>, ili ga možete potpuno promijeniti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:380
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following options in the <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Numeration</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu can be used to "
"change the numeration shown:"
msgstr ""
"Sljedeće opcije u <menuchoice><guimenu>Prikaz</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Prebrojavanje</guimenuitem></menuchoice>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:382
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>No Numeration</guimenuitem>: if this option is active, no "
"period-numeration will be in effect."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Nema prebrojavanja</guimenuitem>: ako je ova opcija aktivna, "
"prebrojavanje perioda neće biti efektno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:385
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>IUPAC</guimenuitem> (default) is the <firstterm>International "
"Union of Pure and Applied Chemistry</firstterm>. This is an organization "
"which defines most of the standards for chemical concerns. The new IUPAC "
"system numbers each column with Arabic numbers from 1 (one) through 18 "
"(eighteen)."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>IUPAC</guimenuitem> (zadanp) je<firstterm>International Union "
"of Pure and Applied Chemistry</firstterm>.  Ovo je organizacija koja "
"definiše najviše standarda koji se tiču hemije. Novi IUPAC sistem numeriše "
"svaku kolonu arapskim brojem od 1(jedan) do 18(osamnaest)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:391
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>CAS</guimenuitem> is the <firstterm>Chemical Abstracts Service</"
"firstterm>. In the CAS system the letters A and B were designated to main "
"group elements (A) and transition elements (B). Though the <acronym>IUPAC</"
"acronym> numeration is the official, the <acronym>CAS</acronym> numeration "
"is what is still used in classrooms and laboratories."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>CAS</guimenuitem> je <firstterm>Chemical Abstracts Service</"
"firstterm>. U CAS sistemu slova A i B su dodijeljena glavnoj grupi elemenata "
"(A) i prijelaznim elementima (B). Iako je <acronym>IUPAC</acronym>  "
"numeracija oficijalna, <acronym>CAS</acronym>  numeracija se još uvijek "
"koristi u učionicama i laboratorijama."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:396
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guimenuitem>Old IUPAC</guimenuitem> system labeled columns with Roman "
"numerals followed by either the letter <quote>A</quote> or <quote>B</quote>. "
"Columns were numbered such that columns one through seven were numbered "
"<quote>IA</quote> through <quote>VIIA</quote>, columns 8 through 10 were "
"labeled <quote>VIIIA</quote>, columns 11 through 17 were numbered <quote>IB</"
"quote> through <quote>VIIB</quote> and column 18 was numbered <quote>VIII</"
"quote>. Because of the confusion the old IUPAC and the CAS system created, "
"the IUPAC adopted their new system."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Stari IUPAC</guimenuitem>sistem obilježava kolone Rimskim "
"brojevima praćenim slovom  <quote>A</quote> ili <quote>B</quote>. Kolone su "
"numerisane tako da su kolone od jedan do sedam numerisane  <quote>IA</quote> "
"do <quote>VIIA</quote>, kolone 8 do 10 označene sa <quote>VIIIA</quote>, "
"kolone 11 do 17 numerisane sa <quote>IB</quote> do <quote>VIIB</quote> i "
"kolona 19 numerisana sa <quote>VIII</quote> . Zbog zabune koji su stari "
"IUPAC i CAS sistem kreirali IUPAC je usvojio novi sistem."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:405
#, no-c-format
msgid "Color schemes"
msgstr "Šeme boja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:407
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kalzium; can show you which elements are where with regard to their "
"Periodic <quote>block</quote> and <quote>group</quote>, their behavior with "
"acid and which state of matter (&ie; solid/liquid/vapor) they are in at a "
"given temperature."
msgstr ""
"&kalzium; može pokazati koji elementi su gdje obzirom na njihov Periodni "
"<quote>blok</quote> i <quote>grupu</quote>, njihovo ponašanje sa kiselinama "
"i koje stanje materije ( &ie; čvrsto/tečno/gasovito) imaju na datoj "
"temperaturi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:408
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Color schemes can be changed in the <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Scheme</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu, toolbar drop-down list, "
"or <link linkend=\"view_tab\">View</link> tab of the Sidebar."
msgstr ""
"Šeme boja mogu biti promijenjene u <menuchoice><guimenu>Prikaz</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Šeme</guimenuitem></menuchoice> meniju, alatnoj traci ispusti-"
"dolje listi, ili <link linkend=\"view_tab\">Prikaz</link> tabu na traci sa "
"strane."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:410
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Monochrome</guimenuitem>: all the elements have the same color. "
"You can change the default color by choosing <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &kalzium;...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> and "
"going to the <guilabel>Schemes</guilabel> page."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Monohromatski</guimenuitem>: svi elementi imaju istu boju. "
"Možete promijeniti zadanu boju birajući <menuchoice><guimenu>Postavke</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriši &kalzium;...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> i "
"iduči na <guilabel>Šeme</guilabel> stranicu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:414
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenuitem>Blocks</guimenuitem>: displays a color for each block."
msgstr "<guimenuitem>Blokovi</guimenuitem>: prikazuju boju za svaki blok."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:417
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenuitem>Iconic</guimenuitem>: displays icons for each element."
msgstr "<guimenuitem>Ikonski</guimenuitem>: prikazuje ikone za svaki element."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:420
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Family</guimenuitem>: represents each of the nine families with "
"a color."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Porodica</guimenuitem>: prikazuje svaku od devet prodica bojom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:423
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Groups</guimenuitem>: displays a color for each group. A group "
"is a vertical column in the periodic table of the elements. There are 18 "
"groups in the standard periodic table. Elements in a group have similar "
"configurations of their valence shell electrons, which gives them similar "
"properties."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Grupe</guimenuitem>: prikazuje boju za svaku grupu. Grupa je "
"vertikalna kolona u periodnom sistemu elemenata. Postoji 18 grupa u "
"standradnom periodnom sistemu. Elementi u grupu imaju sličnu konfiguraciju "
"njihovih valentnih elektrona, što im daje slična svojstva."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:426
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Colors</guimenuitem>: Nice colors without meaning. (From the "
"<ulink url=\"https://openbabel.org/wiki/Main_Page\">Open Babel</ulink> "
"project)."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
