msgstr "<title>Gradijenti</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:433
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The gradient views displays the elements according to a property you can "
"select below and with a gradient colored scheme. The elements for which the "
"data is not available are displayed in gray."
msgstr ""
"Gradijenti prikazuju elemente prema svojstvu koji možete odabrati ispod i sa "
"gradijent obojenom shemom. Elementi za oje podaci nisu dosutpni su obojeni "
"sivo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:434
#, no-c-format
