#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:662
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This calculator tries to find out the equivalence point of a pH-meter "
"followed titration best fitting it with an hyperbolic tangent. You can also "
"let it solve an equilibrium system of equations and see how the "
"concentration of a species changes in function of another one."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj kalkulator pokušava pronaći ekvivalentnu tačku pH-metra titracije koja "
"najbolje odgovara hiperboličkoj tngenti. MOžete takođe riješiti "
"ekvilibrisjski sistem jednačina i vidjeti kako se koncentracija vrste "
"mijenja u zavisnosti od druge."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:665
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are two tabs on the calculator page, namely:"
msgstr "Dva su tabal na stranici kalkulatora, nazvani:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:670
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Experimental Values"
msgid "Experimental values"
msgstr "Eksperimentalne vrijendnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:672
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You can use this calculator to draw the plot of your experimental data "
#| "obtained during a titration and find out the volume of equivalence. It's "
#| "strongly recommended to insert a even number of points, because of the "
#| "best fit algorithm, sorted by volume (the X axis value)."
msgid ""
"You can use this calculator to draw the plot of your experimental data "
"obtained during a titration and find out the volume of equivalence. It's "
"strongly recommended to insert a even number of points, because of the best "
"fit algorithm, sorted by volume (the <guilabel>X axis:</guilabel> value)."
msgstr ""
"Možete koristiti ovaj kalkulator da crtate podlogu za vaše eksperimentalne "
"podatke dobijene tokom titranja i odrediti zapreminu. Jako je preporučljivo "
"da odaberete paran broj tačaka, zbog najboljeg algoritma, sortirano po "
"zapremini ( x veličina )."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:678
#, no-c-format
msgid "Theoretical Equations"
msgstr "Teorijske jednačine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:680
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can fill the table with the equations you have previously obtained "
"for the chemical equilibrium."
msgstr ""
"Ovdje možete popuniti tabelu sa jednačina koje ste prethodno dobili za "
"hemijski ekvilibrum."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:683
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For example, if you have this reaction <emphasis>A + B -> C + D</emphasis> "
"then you will have the equation <emphasis>K=(C*D)/(A*B)</emphasis> so you "
"must write <userinput>K</userinput> in the <guilabel>Parameter</guilabel> "
"column and <userinput>(C*D)/(A*B)</userinput> in the <guilabel>Value</"
"guilabel> column. If you want to assign a known value to a parameter you can "
"simply write the numeric value in the <guilabel>Value</guilabel> field."
msgstr ""
"Na primjer ako imate ovu reakciju <emphasis>A + B -> C + D</emphasis> tada "
"ćete imati ovu jednačinu <emphasis>K=(C*D)/(A*B)</emphasis> pa morate "
"napisati <userinput>K</userinput> u <guilabel>Parametar</guilabel> koloni i "
"<userinput>(C*D)/(A*B)</userinput> u  <guilabel>Vrijednost</guilabel> "
"koloni.. Ako želite dodijeliti poznatu virjednost parametra možete "
"jednostavno napisati brojčanu vrijednost u  <guilabel>Vrijednost</guilabel> "
"polje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:686
#, no-c-format
msgid "For example, you can use the system"
msgstr "Na primjer možete koristiti sistem"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:690
#, no-c-format
msgid "A=(C*D)/(B*K)"
msgstr "A=(C*D)/(B*K)"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:693
#, no-c-format
msgid "K=10^-3"
msgstr "K=10^-3"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:696
#, no-c-format
msgid "C=OH"
msgstr "C=OH"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:699
#, no-c-format
msgid "OH=(10^-14)/H"
msgstr "OH=(10^-14)/H"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:702
#, no-c-format
msgid "H=10^-4"
msgstr "H=10^-4"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:705
#, no-c-format
msgid "B=6*(10^-2)"
msgstr "B=6*(10^-2)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:707
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Then you have to write <userinput>D</userinput> as <guilabel>X axis</"
#| "guilabel> and <userinput>A</userinput> as <guilabel>Y axis</guilabel>: so "
#| "you will find out how the concentration of A changes as a function of D "
#| "concentration."
msgid ""
"Then you have to write <userinput>D</userinput> as <guilabel>X axis:</"
"guilabel> and <userinput>A</userinput> as <guilabel>Y axis:</guilabel>: so "
"you will find out how the concentration of A changes as a function of D "
"concentration."
msgstr ""
"Onda morate napisati <userinput>D</userinput> kao <guilabel>X osa</guilabel> "
"i <userinput>A</userinput> kao <guilabel>Y osa</guilabel>: pa ćete vidjeti "
"kako se koncentracija od A mijenja u funkciji od koncentracije B."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:711
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please don't use parenthesis for exponents: <userinput>10^-3</userinput> is "
"correct, while <userinput>10^(-3)</userinput> is wrong."
msgstr ""
"Molimo da ne koristite zagrade za eksponente :  <userinput>10^-3</userinput> "
"je tačno, dok <userinput>10^(-3)</userinput> je pogrešno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:718
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The results can be visualized by pressing <guibutton>Draw Plot</"
#| "guibutton> button. The plot shows in red the curve that comes from "
#| "theoretical equations, in blue the experimental points, and in green the "
#| "approximated curve for experimental points. You can save the plot as SVG "
#| "image."
msgid ""
"The results can be visualized by pressing <guibutton>Draw Plot</guibutton> "
"button. The plot shows in red the curve that comes from theoretical "
"equations, in blue the experimental points, and in green the approximated "
"curve for experimental points. You can save the plot as &SVG; image."
msgstr ""
"Rezutati se mogu vijdeti pritiskom na <guibutton>Navrtaj podlogu</guibutton> "
"dugme. Podloga pokazazuje krivu u crvenom koja dolazi od teorijskih "
"jedanačina, plavom eksperientalne tačke, i zeleno približnu krivu "
"eksperimentalnih tačaka. Možete spremiti crtež kao SVG sliku."

