#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:920
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "In the <guilabel>Units</guilabel> tab, you can choose the units for "
#| "temperature, length and energy. You can select if you prefer "
#| "electronvolts (eV), kilojoule per mole (kJ/mol) or joule per mole (J/mol) "
#| "by default. For length set picometers (pm), nanometers (nm) or Ångström "
